data.description: Enter into the living room of this spacious 2 story home, leading you into an open concept kitchen and dinning area.  First floor includes a flex room that can be used as a second living room, formal dinning room, office, game room or adjust it to your personal life style. Laundry room and a powder room are also conveniently located on the first floor. All 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms are located on the second floor. Home includes refrigerated air, quartz countertops and stainless steel refrigerator in the kitchen, updated lighting fixtures and raised backyard wall.
